Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.43,0:00:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.98,0:00:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.05,0:00:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:00:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.06,0:00:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.01,0:01:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.31,0:01:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.22,0:01:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.47,0:01:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.54,0:01:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.71,0:01:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.31,0:01:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.05,0:02:04.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yuba" "Erumalu" "Nanohana" "Katorea"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years have passed since\Na single drop of rain fell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.19,0:01:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the kingdom of oases.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.96,0:02:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing hope beyond turmoil,\Nthe people took up weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The burning land is now\Nenveloped by a sad bellowing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.11,0:02:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a mighty swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The once-green city of\NErumalu now lies in ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.98,0:02:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To stop the rebel army, Luffy and\Ncompany now head into the desert
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.02,0:02:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for Yuba, the oasis town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.39,0:02:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Adventure in the Country of Sand! The\NMonsters that Live in the Scorching Land"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burning up...\NSweat won't even come out...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit moaning so much, Luffy.\NYou'll only tire yourself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess he's not listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go on...\NI can't take hot weather...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine in cold weather, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 'cause of all that fur...\NYou should take off that animal suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that, you jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make fun of reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! Don't turn big!\NOr else I won't pull ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you calling a monster,\NHumongo-Nose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be stupid!\NI-I'll have you know this nose--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just turn back already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem to be having\Na hard time, Vivi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was born and raised here,\Nso it doesn't bother me much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what's with all these hills?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured a desert would be more flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a very old desert,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so some sand dunes here\Nare over 300 meters high.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Three hundred meters?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder this is like\Nclimbing mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.48,0:04:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too much... It's so hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one drink, Luffy.\NJust one mouthful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drink so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have some, too!\NThat was 13 mouthfuls just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! You just had some! I'm next!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fighting!\NYou'll only waste strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But she started it!\N--It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! This is because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so greedy!\NIt's still raw! Don't eat that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! Just a minute,\Nit'll be ready soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, looks pretty good!\N--Get away, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!\NCheapskate! Let us eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so hot during the day!\NWhat's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With nothing to block\Nout the temperature,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the desert scorches during the day\Nbut falls below freezing at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The desert is fraught\Nwith unpredictable dangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Look at all those stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you see stars\Non your winter island?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winter island skies are always\Ncovered with thick snow clouds,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I've never seen\Nso many stars before!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the luxury of\Nlooking at stars right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cold weather doesn't bother me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you wear\Nsuch a warm suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.26,0:05:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help that you're so fluffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit making fun of reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper. Don't turn big.\NWe need your warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.94,0:05:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Warm, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a real surprise for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean Luffy-san.\NI was surprised too, at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's that he isn't captain-like,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or that normal pirate captains are\Nrespected by their crewmates...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just this afternoon, a simple\Ndrink of water caused that big fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The longer I've been with them,\Nthe more I've come to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how Luffy does things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't changed a bit\Nsince he was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite how he seems,\Npeople always gather around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he's my little brother,\Nhe has a mysterious charm to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. You already knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He and I do go way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were worried that\NI was concerned, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But it looks like I didn't\Nneed to worry after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! I found a shrimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a shrimp?! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:06:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Shrimp don't live in the desert!\N--See?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:06:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right!\NIs it a "desert shrimp"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It looks yummy!\N--Hey, now! Are they edible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably! Crawfish are edible, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a real shrimp before!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.87,0:07:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Luffy-san! Throw that away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That'd be a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a scorpion! It's small\Nbut it's very poisonous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die if it stings you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. It's not edible? How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You can have it.\N--Don't give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.\NI should've mentioned it earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's... coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is the wind picking up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hide behind the rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A storm! A sandstorm is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.61,0:08:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?! Deserts are nothing but storms!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to mention it, but sandstorms\Nare one of the desert's dangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mention these things sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't people get some rest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Sanji! Let's have a lunch!\NA Pirate Boxed Lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.99,0:09:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet. Not until Vivi-chan says so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Vivi! Let's eat!\NI'm out of strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're only one-tenth of\Nthe way to Yuba, Luffy-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so dumb! Haven't\Nyou heard of this proverb?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.78,0:09:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If you're hungry, eat!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You liar! Quit making stuff up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do you say we take a\Nbreak at the next rocks we find?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Let's hurry to the next rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever wins rock-paper-scissors\Nhas to carry everyone's stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit deciding things!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't the loser carry the stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey! You went after!\N--Woohoo! I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Heavy... So heavy... And hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won rock-paper-scissors,\Nso why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you won.\NNow shut up and haul.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drop it, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rocks spotted a small ways ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For reals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Break time! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shade! Feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get you a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He's coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's lots of hurt birds\Nthat can't move! Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.75,0:11:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Alright! Let's go, Chopper!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta help the birds!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Birds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Luffy-san! Don't tell\Nme these birds are--!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.72,0:11:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All our stuff is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been had...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth! There really\Nwere dying birds here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I should've\Nmentioned it earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warusagi birds are\N"desert bandits" that trick travelers
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.23,0:12:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and steal their belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Birds playing dead?!\NThat's dishonest!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's how they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They tricked me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Is that all you can\Nsay for yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were three days\Nof provisions in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you just had to let some\Ndamn birds steal everyone's stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,smack in the middle of this desert?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How're we supposed to cross the\Ndesert without food or water now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my fault. They tricked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your brain less than a bird's?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.67,0:12:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At times like this,\Nit's best to let them have it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a short break.\NThis heat is what has them fuming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:13:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll manage food-wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing that'll kill us.\NLet's just put it out of our minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Just thinking makes me thirstier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us our stuff back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san! Don't chase them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Will you be\Nable to come back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! You can't get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.38,0:14:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mystery desert plant?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You want me to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing you didn't get eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The birds got away while\NI was beating these guys up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The desert sure is full\Nof strange creatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, camel. What're you doing\Nout here all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.83,0:15:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's taking Luffy so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Do you think he got lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a horrible sense of\Ndirection but always has to run off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are so many desert\Ndangers he doesn't know about...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y'know, isn't he hungry\Nfrom not eating anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a lost cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.54,0:16:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For my little brother's ineptness.\NI apologize for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck finding him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.52,0:16:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this rumbling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another sandstorm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait! That's--!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... it couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he on a camel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?! What's that chasing him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.99,0:17:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems more like\Nsomething's in the sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Sandora Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A what now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the largest of the\Nreptiles living in the desert
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they wait under the\Nsand for their prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have sharp claws and fangs,\Nbut they hardly ever use them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:18:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason being that they tend\Nto swallow their prey whole
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.25,0:18:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because they're so large!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really does have a gift\Nfor attracting trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Setting aside the camel for the moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what star was he born under to be\Nable to attract trouble like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Camel! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy! Is it too much for you?!\N--We'll lend a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I brought some meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes, lizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Tatsu...\N--paule...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--...Maki!\N--...Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You didn't have to go that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they're fighting,\Nyou almost pity the monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to mention it,\Nbut Sandora Dragons hunt in pairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mention these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ace!\N--Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay. If that's what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out! These rocks\Nare natural frying pans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's with the camel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.89,0:19:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was getting eaten by a mystery\Nplant when I was chasing the birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem to be a wild camel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. It even has a saddle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:19:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! He gave me a ride\Nwhen I escaped from Katorea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.22,0:20:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great! We can ride it?!\NThat'll make things easier!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that'll be a real help!\NLooks like it could carry two people!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camels do go hand-in-hand with deserts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll be the first one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I am a freedom-loving,\Nhard-boiled, compassionate camel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for helping me out of that pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can give you a lift,\Nbut no men allowed!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's a punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You let Chopper ride you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm manly!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Quit being stupid!\N--Why, you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!\NMy crewmates are so ill-bred!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.29,0:20:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good boy!\NWhat should we call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.13,0:20:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Idiot!\N--Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doofus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:20:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Lashes" it is, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh, that's the weirdest one of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Get on, Vivi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can still walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pervy camel! Pervy camel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pervy camel! Pervy camel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we should make a little better time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to get to Yuba as fast as\Nwe can to talk to the rebel army!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giddyup, Lashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.66,0:21:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, guys! If you get separated,\Nyou'll never leave the desert alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit being stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.46,0:21:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like this side of Nami-san, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After them! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Get on, Chopper!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.19,0:22:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the adventurers\NI dreamed of when I was a child
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.04,0:22:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I continue on to the ends of emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.11,0:22:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I scoop up my hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.08,0:22:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the sand and time\Nthat spills from them
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.72,0:22:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,show me that this is\Nwhat I was born to do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.73,0:22:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue swimming\Nat a near-tumbling speed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we wash up someday\Non a white sandy beach
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.58,0:22:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no one knows about
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.97,0:23:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So hot...\N--Nami-san! How far did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.14,0:23:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're completely separated now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.20,0:23:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\NI don't see Ace, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.27,0:23:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Do you think he got separated?\N--What a troublesome big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.31,0:23:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?! What's that?!\N--Do you see Nami's group?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.31,0:23:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ship! A pirate ship in the sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Enter the Desert Pirates!\NThe Men Who Live Freely"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.09,0:23:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.42,0:23:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
[Events]
